reviewText: Not at all what the description of the story implied.  So much chattering.  I was waiting for the mysterious house with hidden rooms to take me out of the boredom of the players conversation...never happened.  If you enjoy old mysteries with ambiance, skip this one.
I've always loved old haunted house movies and was very pleased with The Door With Seven Locks.  Here's hoping I manage to find a few more of the same genre.
